// CAPZ (cluster-api-provider-azure) bundles webhook code in its api/v1beta1 package
// that uses a controller-runtime webhook API incompatible with v0.23+. This module only
// uses controller-runtime's pkg/client (Get/List/Patch/Create), which is stable across
// versions. This replace pins controller-runtime to a version compatible with CAPZ v1.21.0
// (the same version used by HyperShift).
replace sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime => sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.20.4
